{"title":"Hexo 网站初始化","date":"2022-04-25T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年4月25日","L":"2022/04/25","MM-DD":"04-25"},"thumbnail":"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2022/04/25/d40b4849a173fada.png","link":"hexo-web-site-inti","tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2022-04-25T07:19:19.222Z","content":"<p>第一步</p>\n<p>初始化：<code>hexo init</code></p>\n<p>安装 主题<br>\n使用的主题：<code>inside</code><br>\n地址：<code>https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li>进入博客目录 <code>project/</code> , 执行以下命令：</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-theme-inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>配置：<code>project/_config.yml</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">inside</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>创建主题文件：<code>project/_config.inside.yml</code></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/omnibingo/talk2.it\">https://github.com/omnibingo/talk2.it</a></p>\n","next":{"title":"Hello World","link":"hello-world"},"plink":"http://l-zm.com/hexo-web-site-inti/","reading_time":"85 字约 1 分钟"}